Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Dumeles Elementary School in the Municipality of San Enrique, Province of Iloilo, to Don Pedro M. Fernandez Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 801
An Act Changing the Name of the Dumeles Elementary School in the Municipality of San Enrique, Province of Iloilo, to Don Pedro M. Fernandez Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Dumeles Elementary School in the Municipality of San Enrique, Province of Iloilo, is changed to Don Pedro M. Fernandez Elementary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
